Source: libmutil
Priority: optional
Section: devel
Maintainer: Johan Bilien <jobi@via.ecp.fr>
Uploaders: Mikael Magnusson <mikma@users.sourceforge.net>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 4.0.0), dpatch, autotools-dev
Standards-Version: 3.6.1

Package: libmutil0
Section: libs
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: different utilities classes for portable C++ development
 libmutil contains different classes useful for C++ programming, mostly
 string handling, cryptography and portable thread control. It is used
 by the minisip SIP user agent.
 .
 This package contains the libmutil0 runtime library.

Package: libmutil-dev
Architecture: any
Depends: libmutil0 (= ${Source-Version})
Description: different utilities classes for portable C++ development
 libmutil contains different classes useful for C++ programming, mostly
 string handling, cryptography and portable thread control. It is used
 by the minisip SIP user agent.
 .
 This package contains the header files and static library needed to
 compile applications that use libmutil0.
